OL,3,CGovernment confirms cut in migrant
OL,4,Cnumbers at ex-RAF base
OL,6,FThe government says a former RAF
OL,7,Fairbase will house a maximum of 800
OL,8,Fmigrants ` down from an initial limit
OL,9,Fof 2,000.
OL,11,FIn a letter to Gainsborough MP Sir
OL,12,FEdward Leigh, Home Office minister Tom
OL,13,FPursglove confirmed the "regular
OL,14,Foccupancy" at RAF Scampton, near ,
OL,15,Fwould be capped.
OL,17,FUp to 2,000 male asylum seekers were
OL,18,Fdue to be housed on the former base,
OL,19,Fwhich was once home to the famous
OL,20,FDambusters squadron.
