OL,6,FNone have moved in so far.
OL,8,FMr Pursglove said about 300 extra bed
OL,9,Fspaces may be used for "short and
OL,10,Fdefined periods" if required.
OL,12,FHe added: "It is important that we are
OL,13,Freducing hotel costs and delivering
OL,14,Four asylum accommodation sites in a
OL,15,Fsafe and orderly manner.
OL,17,F"Implementing a cap on occupation
OL,18,Fdemonstrates that our priority is
OL,19,Flistening to local concerns,
OL,20,Fmitigating impacts, and managing the
OL,21,Fsite safely."
