OL,6,FWest Lindsey District Council (WLDC)
OL,7,Fhad drawn up a #300 million plan to
OL,8,Fregenerate the site, which was put on
OL,9,Fhold when the Government announced its
OL,10,Fmigrant plans last year.
OL,12,FSir Edward said he was "pleased" at
OL,13,Fthe news but added he was "seeking
OL,14,Ffurther reassurance that they will be
OL,15,Fprohibited from going onto the former
OL,16,Fmarried quarters and that the
OL,17,Faccommodation they are housed in will
OL,18,Fbe temporary".
